Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
itml.agents.Agent This class provides the base itml.agents.Agent type, from which other agents should subclass.
itml.agents.AgentChicken Example agent: This agent always tries to run away from the other agent (chicken, chicken, ...).
itml.agents.AgentLazy Example agent: This agent is simply a sitting duck.
itml.agents.AgentManual Example agent: This agent allows a user to play as an agent (prompted for actions).
itml.agents.AgentRandom Example agent: This agent picks a random legal action.
itml.agents.AgentTerminator Example agent: This agent is very aggressive, runs directly towards the opponent and once the opponent is in range attacks.
itml.simulator.Battle This class provides the type itml.simulator.Battle, which takes care of the logistics regarding conducting battles.
itml.BattleSim The main class, drives the training and competition matches.
itml.cards.Card This class provides the type itml.cards.Card, which represents a playing card for determining an action a player can make.
itml.cards.CardAttackCardinal This class implements a itml.cards.Card that attacks the square the agent is on as well as the four adjacent cardinal directions.
itml.cards.CardAttackDiagonal This class implements a itml.cards.Card that attacks the square the agent is on as well as the four adjacent diagonal directions.
itml.cards.CardAttackLong This class implements a itml.cards.Card that attacks the square the agent is on as well as the next two squares (back and forth) horizontally.
itml.simulator.CardDeck This class provides the type itml.simulator.CardDeck, which represents a deck of playing cards (itml.cards.Card).
itml.cards.CardDefend This class implements a itml.cards.Card that (partially) defends off the opponents attack.
itml.cards.CardLeapLeft This class implements a movement itml.cards.Card where the agents moves two squares to the left.
itml.cards.CardLeapRight This class implements a movement itml.cards.Card where the agents moves two squares to the right.
itml.cards.CardMoveDown This class implements a movement itml.cards.Card where the agents moves one square down.
itml.cards.CardMoveLeft This class implements a movement itml.cards.Card where the agents moves one square to the left.
itml.cards.CardMoveRight This class implements a movement itml.cards.Card where the agents moves one square to the right.
itml.cards.CardMoveUp This class implements a movement itml.cards.Card where the agents moves one square up.
itml.cards.CardRest This class implements a itml.cards.Card where the agents rests, replenishing its stamina.
itml.simulator.Coordinate This class implements the type itml.simulator.Coordinate, representing two-dimensional indicies (x,y)
itml.simulator.GameLog This class implements the type itml.simulator.GameLog, which is used to record the history of a game (the sequence of states that occur in a battle).
itml.simulator.StateAgent This class implements the type itml.simulator.StateAgent, which keeps track of the state of an agent (i.e., location, stamina, and health).
itml.simulator.StateBattle This class implements the type itml.simulator.StateBattle, which keeps track of the current state of a battle.
